	<description>
		A minimalist physics...racer? The goal is to pull a ball through the levels as quickly as possible without working up so much momentum that you destroy yourself in the process. It's a bit harder than it sounds.
	</description>
	
	<history>
		The original idea for this game was sparked in 2008 or 2009 in a game design and development course. It's since gone through many, <i>many</i> changes. I started development back up in November 2013 and worked on it on and off until now. The game was first publicly shown at GAMCON.
	</history>

	<features>
		<feature>Pixel-perfect collision!</feature>
		<feature>Simulated mass!</feature>
		<feature>Easily make custom levels with your favorite image editing software!</feature>
